	<h3>Teaching</h3>
	<p>
	As one of the main parts of our services we study a topic or section of the Bible. In the future we will put more information in this section. Hopefully, this section can already be useful as an introduction for you if you would like to find out what we have been looking at or as a reminder for those who were there.  If you are new to the Bible or to church then you may find the section more on the Bible.

	<h3>Teaching in Sunday Services</h3>
	<p>
	This section is intended to give you an idea of the subjects that we are looking at in our services. Bible verses are given so that you can look up the references and gain a better understanding, or be reminded, of what the message was about. Click <a href="/teaching/bible.mhtml">here</a> if you aren't that familiar with the Bible and would like a short introduction. Also, if references like "2 Peter 1:3-4" don't make much sense to you then have a look at Bible and Bible references for an explanation.

	<h3>Mornings</h3>
